---
title: Provençal Herbed Chicken with Burst Tomatoes and Cheesy Pesto Orzo
description: Here’s a meal that packs plenty of sophistication for the adults while also keeping things kid-friendly. It features chicken breasts seasoned with herbs de Provence and a Parmesan pesto orzo—in other words, tender white meat with a side of cheesy pasta. For the veg, there’s grape tomatoes simmered in a sauce that makes them extra flavorful, juicy, and guaranteed to please.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/provencal-herbed-chicken-4ad07dc7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/provencal-herbed-chicken-5ca4f6b9c445fa4969630c52-e052d82b.pdf
